></p>','','','','','');
INSERT INTO `p8_cms_item_article_addon` (`id`,`iid`,`page`,`addon_title`,`addon_frame`,`addon_summary`,`ip`,`last_update_ip`,`timestamp`,`content`,`custom_f`,`custom_g`,`custom_h`,`custom_i`,`custom_j`) VALUES ('2947','3772','1','','/ewebeditor/sysimage/icon16/xls.gif','根据《盐城市第一人民医院2022年公开招聘编外专业技术人员公告》精神，因部分岗位无人报名及报名通过资格审核人数未达规定的开考比例，经核准，现对相关招聘岗位（计划）予以取消（核减）和降低开考比例，具体情况见附件。原报考岗位被取消的应聘人员可在2022年9月9日上','172.16.1.2','172.16.1.2','1662623734','<p align=\"left\" style=\'background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 28.5pt; text-indent: 32.25pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"background: white; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 方正仿宋_GBK; font-size: 15.5pt;\">根据《盐城市第一人民医院<span>2022</span>年公开招聘编外专业技术人员公告》精神，因部分岗位无人报名及报名通过资格审核人数未达规定的开考比例，经核准，现对相关招聘岗位（计划）予以取消（核减）和降低开考比例，具体情况见附件。</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\'background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 28.5pt; text-indent: 32.25pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"background: white; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 方正仿宋_GBK; font-size: 15.5pt;\">原报考岗位被取消的应聘人员可在<span>2022</span>年<span>9</span>月<span>9</span>日上午<span>10:00</span>点前改报其他符合条件的岗位（改报方式：网上报名，报名邮箱<span>:798982768@qq.com</span>），逾期视为自动放弃。</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\'background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 28.5pt; text-indent: 32.25pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"background: white; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 方正仿宋_GBK; font-size: 15.5pt;\">特此公告。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span>&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span>&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span><img border=\"0\" src=\"/ewebeditor/sysimage/icon16/xls.gif\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"/ewebeditor/uploadfile/file/2022/09/08/20220908155521595.xls\">附件 盐城市第一人民医院2022年公开招聘编外专业技术人员取消（核减）和降低开考比例部分岗位招聘计划表.xls</a></span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span>&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span>&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"right\" style=\'background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: right; line-height: 28.5pt; text-indent: 32.25pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"background: white; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 方正仿宋_GBK; font-size: 15.5pt;\">盐城市第一人民医院</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"right\" style=\'background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: right; line-height: 28.5pt; text-indent: 32.25pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"background: white; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 方正仿宋_GBK; font-size: 15.5pt;\">2022</span><span style=\"background: white; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 方正仿宋_GBK; font-size: 15.5pt;\">年<span>9</span>月<span>8</span>日</span></p>\r\n<p></p>','','','','','');
INSERT INTO `p8_cms_item_article_addon` (`id`,`iid`,`page`,`addon_title`,`addon_frame`,`addon_summary`,`ip`,`last_update_ip`,`timestamp`,`content`,`custom_f`,`custom_g`,`custom_h`,`custom_i`,`custom_j`) VALUES ('2948','3773','1','','','盐城市第一人民医院北院区医技、门诊楼消防管网改造工程已具备招标条件，项目所需资金来源为自筹资金并已落实。现通过公开招标方式邀请潜在投标人参加本项目的投标报名。现就有关事项公告如下：一、招标人名称：盐城市第一人民医院 二、招标代理机构：江苏双清工程造价','172.16.1.2','172.16.1.2','1662691783','<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 22pt; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">盐城市第一人民医院北院区医技、门诊楼消防管网改造工程已具备招标条件，项目所需资金来源为自筹资金并已落实。现通过公开招标方式邀请潜在投标人参加本项目的投标报名。现就有关事项公告如下：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 22pt; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">一、招标人名称：</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">盐城市</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">第一人民医院<span>&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 22pt; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">二、招标代理机构：江苏双清工程造价咨询有限公司 </span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 24.1pt; font-family: \"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><b><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">三、项目概况：</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">、工程名称：盐城市第一人民医院北院区医技、门诊楼消防管网改造工程。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">、工程地点：</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">盐城市第一人民医院北院区</span><span style=\"color: black; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"color: black; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">3</span><span style=\"color: black; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">、招标规模：工程造价约</span><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">6.5</span><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">万元</span><span style=\"color: black; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 22pt; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"color: black; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">4</span><span style=\"color: black; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">、招标范围及内容：盐城市第一人民医院北院区医技、门诊楼消防管网改造工程的施工，具体内容详见招标人提供的图纸及工程量清单。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"color: black; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">5</span><span style=\"color: black; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">、工期要求：</span><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">20</span><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">日历天</span><span style=\"color: black; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">，具体开工日期以招标人的通知为准。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"color: black; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">6</span><span style=\"color: black; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">、质量标准：符合国家“合格”标准。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 24.1pt; font-family: \"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><b><span style=\"color: black; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">四、投标人资格要求：</span></b></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 22pt; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">、投标人<span style=\"background: white; color: black;\">须具有建设行政主管部门核发的消防设施工程专业承包二级及以上资质的独立法人，并具有有效的安全生产许可证</span>。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">、项目负责人资格类别和等级<span>:</span>项目负责人须<span style=\"background: white; color: black;\">提供机电工程专业二级及以上建造师注册证书和安全生产考核合格证（<span>B</span>类）</span>。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">、本次招标不接受联合体投标。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">4</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">、财务要求：投标人应具有独立订立合同的能力，未处于财产被接管、冻结和破产状态。<span>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">5</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">、信誉要求：投标人没有被国家、江苏省省级有关部门及盐城市级有关部门暂停招投标或市场准入资格且在公示处罚期内。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">6</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">、投标申请人须保证委托代理人、项目负责人均为本单位的正式职工，并确保从投标截止之日当月向前连续<span>6</span>个月均已在本单位缴纳养老保险（例：如开标日期为<span>2020</span>年<span>7</span>月的某一天，则投标单位需保证以上人员<span>2020</span>年<span>1-6</span>月养老保险均在本单位缴纳）。投标时无须提供证明材料，如有质疑或招标人要求，再按要求提供相关证明材料。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 24.1pt; font-family: \"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><b><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">五、招标文件获取：</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">请符合要求的潜在投标人于</span><span style=\"color: blue; font-size: 12pt;\">2022</span><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">年</span><span style=\"color: blue; font-size: 12pt;\">9</span><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">月</span><span style=\"color: blue; font-size: 12pt;\">9</span><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">日至</span><span style=\"color: blue; font-size: 12pt;\">2022</span><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">年</span><span style=\"color: blue; font-size: 12pt;\">9</span><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">月</span><span style=\"color: blue; font-size: 12pt;\">16</span><span style=\"color: blue; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">日</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">（每日上午</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">8</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">：</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">30</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">时至</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">12</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">：</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">00</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">时，下午</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">14</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">：</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">30</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">时至</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">18</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">：</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">00</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">时）携带单位介绍信原件（或授权委托书原件，注明联系人电话及邮箱）至江苏双清工程造价咨询有限公司（</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">盐城市紫薇广场<span>C</span>区<span>7</span>楼</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">）报名并领取招标文件（联系人：周会计，联系电话：</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">0515-88200706</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">，</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">18705110288</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">）</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">，逾期不再受理。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 24.1pt; font-family: \"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><b><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">六、投标保证金</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">本项目投标保证金<span style=\"color: black;\">为人民币<span>1000</span>元，具体详见招标文件。</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"color: black; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">七、本项目资格审查办法采用<b>资格后审</b>；评标办法采用<b>综合评估法</b>，具体详见招标文件。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"color: black; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">八、本项目严禁挂靠，一经核实挂靠，将被取消投标、中标资格，并按相关规定进行处罚，直至建议有关部门吊销资质证书。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 24.1pt; font-family: \"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><b><span style=\"color: black; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">九、联系方式</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"color: black; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">招标人：盐城市第一</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">人民医院</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">地<span>&nbsp; </span>址：盐城市人民南路<span>66</span>号</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">联系人：</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">周先生</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">电<span>&nbsp; </span>话：</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">13905102015</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"color: black; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">招标代理机构：江苏双清工程</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">造价咨询有限公司<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">地<span>&nbsp; </span>址：盐城市紫薇广场<span>C</span>区<span>7</span>楼<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">联系人：张先生<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">电<span>&nbsp; </span>话：<span>0515-88200316</span>、<span>13515130964</span></span></p>','','','','','');
INSERT INTO `p8_cms_item_article_addon` (`id`,`iid`,`page`,`addon_title`,`addon_frame`,`addon_summary`,`ip`,`last_update_ip`,`timestamp`,`content`,`custom_f`,`custom_g`,`custom_h`,`custom_i`,`custom_j`) VALUES ('2949','3774','1','','','盐城市第一人民医院主院区及北院区安检设备采购及安装项目已具备招标条件，项目所需资金来源为自筹资金并已落实。现通过公开招标方式邀请潜在投标人参加本项目的投标报名。现就有关事项公告如下：一、江苏双清工程造价咨询有限公司受招标人委托具体负责本项目的招标事宜','172.16.1.2','172.16.1.2','1662691828','<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">盐城市第一人民医院主院区及北院区安检设备采购及安装项目已具备招标条件，项目所需资金来源为自筹资金并已落实。现通过公开招标方式邀请潜在投标人参加本项目的投标报名。现就有关事项公告如下：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12pt;\">一、</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">江苏双清工程造价咨询有限公司受招标人委托具体负责本项目的招标事宜。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12pt;\">二、</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">符合本项目招标公告资格要求的投标的申请人均可参加该项目投标。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">三、项目概况</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12pt;\">1</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">、项目名称：盐城市第一人民医院主院区及北院区安检设备采购及安装项目</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12pt;\">2</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">、工程地点：盐城市第一人民医院院内<span style=\"color: blue;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12pt;\">3</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">、工程规模：<span style=\"color: blue;\">约</span></span><span style=\"color: blue; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12pt;\">22.9</span><span style=\"color: blue; line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">万元</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12pt;\">4</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">、</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">质量标准：符合国家及行业规范“合格”标准，质保期<span>2</span>年。投标人需确保选用的产品符合医院安全管理工作需要，符合招标文件、报价清单中参数要求，符合招标人的实际工作需要，若投标选用的产品不能达到招标文件及甲方的实际使用需要，由中标人无偿整改到位，所以费用由中标人承担。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12pt;\">5</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">、供货要求：</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12pt;\">20</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">日历天</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">，具体开工日期以招标人的通知为准</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">四、标段划分及招标内容</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12pt;\">1</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">、招标内容：盐城市第一人民医院主院区及北院区安检设备采购及安装项目，包含但不限于采购、供应、安装、调试、售后等相关伴随服务，具体数量及规格等要求详见工程量清单，招标人保留对上述工程规模进行适当调整的权利。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">五、投标人主要资格要求</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12pt;\">1</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">、投标人资质要求：投标人具备建设行政主管部门核发的电子与智能化工程专业承包二级及以上资质或有效期内的建筑智能化工程设计与施工一体化二级及以上资质，且有安全生产许可证的独立法人企业。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12pt;\">2</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">、投标人须保证项目负责人及代理人均为本单位的正式职工，并确保从投标截止之日当月向前连续</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12pt;\">6</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">个月均已在本单位缴纳养老保险（例：如开标日期为</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12pt;\">2020</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">年</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12pt;\">7</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">月的某一天，则投标单位需保证以上人员</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12pt;\">2020</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">年</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12pt;\">1-6</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">月养老保险均在本单位缴纳）。投标时无须提供证明材料，如有质疑或招标人要求，再按要求提供相关证明材料。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12pt;\">3</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">、本次招标不接受联合体投标。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12pt;\">4</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">、财务要求：投标人应具有独立订立合同的能力，未处于财产被接管、冻结和破产状态。</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12pt;\">5</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">、信誉要求：投标人没有被国家、江苏省省级有关部门及盐城市级有关部门暂停招投标或市场准入资格且在公示处罚期内。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">六、投标保证金：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">本项目投标保证金为人民币叁仟元整，具体交纳方式详见招标文件约定。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">七、本项目评标办法采用“综合评估法”。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">八、投标报名及招标文件领取时间和地点</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">请符合要求的潜在投标人于</span><span style=\"color: blue; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12pt;\">2022</span><span style=\"color: blue; line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">年</span><span style=\"color: blue; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12pt;\">9</span><span style=\"color: blue; line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">月</span><span style=\"color: blue; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12pt;\">9</span><span style=\"color: blue; line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">日至</span><span style=\"color: blue; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12pt