an style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">、项目名称：盐城市儿童医院一键报警建设项目</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12pt;\">2</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">、工程地点：</span><span style=\"color: blue; line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">盐城市儿童医院院内</span><span style=\"color: blue; line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12pt;\">3</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">、工程规模：约</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12pt;\">3.1</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">万元。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12pt;\">4</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">、</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">质量标准：符合国家及行业规范“合格”标准，质保期<span>2</span>年。投标人需确保选用的产品符合医院安全管理工作需要，符合招标文件、报价清单中参数要求，符合招标人的实际工作需要，若投标选用的产品不能达到招标文件及甲方的实际使用需要，由中标人无偿整改到位，所以费用由中标人承担。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12pt;\">5</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">、供货要求：</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12pt;\">15</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">日历天</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">，具体开工日期以招标人的通知为准</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">四、标段划分及招标内容</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12pt;\">1</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">、招标内容：盐城市儿童医院一键报警建设项目，包含但不限于采购、供应、安装、调试、售后等相关伴随服务，具体数量及规格等要求详见工程量清单，招标人保留对上述工程规模进行适当调整的权利。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">五、投标人主要资格要求</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12pt;\">1</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">、投标人资质要求：投标申请人必须是在中国境内注册，有独立完成本项目所有工作的能力的独立法人，且具有省公安部门颁发的保安服务许可证。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12pt;\">2</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">、投标人拟派项目负责人须具备保安职业资格二级及以上资质，必须为本单位正式职工，需提供劳动合同及近</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12pt;\">6</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">个月由社保机构出具的社保缴纳证明（加盖社保中心章或社保中心参保缴费证明电子专用章）。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12pt;\">3</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">、本次招标不接受联合体投标。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12pt;\">4</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">、财务要求：投标人应具有独立订立合同的能力，未处于财产被接管、冻结和破产状态。</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12pt;\">5</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">、信誉要求：投标人没有被国家、江苏省省级有关部门及盐城市级有关部门暂停招投标或市场准入资格且在公示处罚期内。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">六、投标保证金：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">本项目投标保证金为人民币伍佰元整，具体交纳方式详见招标文件约定。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justi